  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8a\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The postal workers' layoffs also hit the hills",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "While the Department of Posts has announced that postal employees should work three days a week, post office employees in many areas including Attan in the highlands are still on strike today (04.07.2022) demanding that Saturday be included in those three days.",
        "Due to problems including fuel, the Department of Posts has taken steps to limit the work.",
        "In that regard, the Department of Posts had recently announced that postal employees should work only on Tuesdays, Wednesdays and Thursdays in the week.",
        "In this situation, the post office employees in the highlands are continuing their strike demanding that Saturday be included in the three days given to them.",
        "The postal workers have said that this strike which started last Wednesday will continue till the 11th.",
        "However, due to this strike, postal service and office correspondence cannot be carried out in the highlands and people are unable to transact."
      ],
